introduction.para: The #UNKNOWN! error indicates a unknown data type that is not currently supported in this version of Excel. If you need to work with this data type, consider upgrading to a newer version of Office.https://products.office.com/buy/compare-microsoft-office-products

alert.para: July 31, 2018: This feature is being made available to customers on a gradual basis over several days or weeks. It will first be available to Office Insiderhttps://products.office.com/office-insider participants, and later to Office 365https://products.office.com/buy/compare-microsoft-office-products subscribers. If you are an Office 365 subscriber, make sure you have the latest version of Office.
